metadata.name: Do You Remember the Snow, Starling?
metadata.description:
...Do you remember the snow, Starling?
We used to play around as kids.
...Do you remember the snow, Starling?
You said you'd stay and be legit.

We're exiles in your mind you can't burn us away,
We may be far behind but you know we're here to stay.

...Do you remember the snow, Starling?
